reviewText: Not complete songs. Only breaks and some accompaniment. Maybe another DVD set will be released that covers what is missing from the songs covered here? I wish that the parts of the songs that were not covered on the DVDs where at least provided in TAB on the PDF.

This Blind Blake stuff is a real challenge, I bought it mainly to learn Too Tight Rag, which is 1/2 way through disc 2 but found I had to go back to the start of disc 1 to begin to nail some of the techniques before moving on. There will be a lot of wood shedding to get through these lessons.
